xxl.core.relational.metaData

Class TupleMetaData

  • java.lang.Object
    • xxl.core.relational.metaData.TupleMetaData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ResultSetMetaData, Wrapper, ExtendedResultSetMetaData

    public class TupleMetaData
extends Object
implements ExtendedResultSetMetaData
    An object that can be used to get and set information about the types and properties of the columns inside a tuple. It is a ready-to-use implementation of ResultSetMetaData .

    Please note that TupleMetaData contains meta data for each component.
    See Also:
    ColumnMetaData
